snippet.title: Play Monster Fight on WAX Blockchain | NFT Game Release Date Revealed
snippet.description:
Get your monsters ready. Play Adventure Mode soon... Date reveal is in the teaser. Adventure mode will be downloadable at first. Browser version for Adventure Mode needs to be optimized and may come at a later date.

https://monsterfi.io
